snippet.title: PAC-MAN™ 99 - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
PAC-MAN™ is back in a new 99-PAC-MAN battle royale! PAC-MAN™ 99 goes live 4/7 at 6 PM PST, exclusively for #NintendoSwitchOnline members!
